"info_title" = "Are you experiencing mobbing in real life?";
"info_body" = "Mobbing is systematic psychological harassment at work: isolation, humiliation, impossible workloads, rumors.\n\nWhat helps:\n• Keep a dated journal of every incident (what, who, witnesses).\n• Save emails and messages — forward them to a private address.\n• Report through official channels in writing.\n• Talk to a doctor — health effects are real and documentable.\n• Consult a labor lawyer; in many countries mobbing is legally recognized.\n• You are not alone, and it is not your fault.\n\nThis game is fiction, but the patterns are real. If they feel familiar, take them seriously.";
